I don't really know how the SR300 camera behave, but I had a similar issue with a D4XX. I'm guessing that you are not specifying precisely enough which device you want to access, and the first one might then be selected by default (which can be your webcam). Maybe try to display a list of the connected devices to understand which one is which.
Here is an idea of the principle (work for D4XX coded in C++) : 
```
// Create a context
